Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是公人大人的女僕？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點動手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萌萌  噗啾
