Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你真遲鈍呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:18.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊是嗎  這是害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:18.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}暄騰鬆軟入口即化的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:22.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}鬆鬆軟軟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}戀愛就像松露一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中悸動不已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}一跳一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:30.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天真得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:33.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}全力突擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向著心愛的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:42.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}給你一心一意的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:06.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}分かるつもりでいたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}広い世界のモーダル
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}今日の行方  終えるだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:17.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}手ほどきも受けたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:21.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}だけど予測不可能な
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}この想いに名前を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:28.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}付けられない  私がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:32.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}マニュアルじゃダメね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:36.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}とけてしまうボーダーライン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}赤と青の夕間暮れ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}いつの間にかキミが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:51.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}心の中と外まで  分からなくさせた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:55.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}トワイライトに消えないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:59.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}私を全部見つめていて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:03.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}きっとこれから  起こるすべてが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:06.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}恋のきっかけでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:10.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}作り笑いじゃ  隠しきれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:15.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}涙や夢も  連れて行ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:18.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}きっと誰もが  うらやむような
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}日々を  キミにあげたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:06.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}還以為能夠理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}廣闊世界的模態
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}完成今天的目標的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:17.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}指導也已經接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:21.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}沒法給這個無法預測的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:28.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}回憶取個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:32.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}叫手冊可不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:36.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}融化的邊界線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}紅色與藍色的黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}不知何時你讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:51.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}覺得由內而外的陌生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:55.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}不要消失在暮光中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:59.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}要看著我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:03.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}之後發生的事情一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:06.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}戀愛的契機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:10.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}強顏歡笑也藏不住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:15.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}淚水和夢想  就把它們帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:18.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}一定有誰會令人羨慕地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}與你度過每一天
